1
00:01:21,520 --> 00:01:22,320
Miss,

2
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:23,320
you're going abroad.

3
00:01:23,320 --> 00:01:25,320
You must take your medicine on time.

4
00:01:26,440 --> 00:01:28,039
When will you come back?

5
00:01:29,760 --> 00:01:30,890
I can't say for sure.

6
00:01:31,720 --> 00:01:32,800
Maybe never.

7
00:01:34,600 --> 00:01:37,720
It's time for me to forget everything here.

8
00:01:41,240 --> 00:01:43,360
I heard from Lu Jingheng that you're leaving,

9
00:01:43,360 --> 00:01:44,620
so I came to see you off.

10
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:54,080
I was seriously ill before,

11
00:01:54,440 --> 00:01:56,200
and I don't remember many things.

12
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,960
I didn't mean to forget you.

13
00:01:59,759 --> 00:02:01,560
You are really important to me.

14
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:03,420
Thank you for being my friend.

15
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:06,500
For what happened before,

16
00:02:06,960 --> 00:02:08,280
I owe you an apology.

17
00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:15,760
Miss, it's about time.

18
00:02:15,760 --> 00:02:17,820
If we don't go, we'll miss the flight.

19
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:26,720
Take care.

20
00:03:16,720 --> 00:03:19,250
Since you came back from seeing Wen Shuyi off,

21
00:03:19,600 --> 00:03:21,000
you've been spacing out.

22
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:24,170
Just ask if you have any questions.

23
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:25,920
I have nothing to ask.

24
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:28,170
If you don't ask now,

25
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:30,660
you won't have a chance later.

26
00:03:32,640 --> 00:03:33,440
Wait.

27
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:39,040
Did you like Wen Shuyi before?

28
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:40,200
No.

29
00:03:40,320 --> 00:03:41,120
No.

30
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:44,040
Then why do the aunts in the Lu family say

31
00:03:44,040 --> 00:03:45,840
you are childhood sweethearts?

32
00:03:46,079 --> 00:03:46,880
Besides,

33
00:03:47,440 --> 00:03:50,079
you're clearly very tolerant towards her.

34
00:03:50,480 --> 00:03:52,079
It's precisely because I don't like her

35
00:03:52,079 --> 00:03:53,680
that I feel even more guilty.

36
00:03:54,640 --> 00:03:56,400
Before Uncle Wen forced her to marry far away,

37
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,930
she actually came to see me.

38
00:03:58,040 --> 00:04:00,880
She wanted me to agree to a fake proposal.

39
00:04:02,880 --> 00:04:05,160
Shuyi, you're in such a hurry to see me.

40
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:06,290
Is something wrong?

41
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:08,840
Jingheng, I have a request.

42
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:11,040
Just tell me.

43
00:04:12,040 --> 00:04:14,120
Lu Jingheng, I want to marry you.

44
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:15,180
Let's get married.

45
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:17,120
What?

46
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:20,839
Jingheng, please help me.

47
00:04:20,959 --> 00:04:22,200
Just pretend.

48
00:04:22,440 --> 00:04:23,520
If you propose,

49
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:25,380
my family will definitely agree.

50
00:04:27,280 --> 00:04:28,410
Get up first, Shuyi.

51
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,410
I won't get up unless you agree.

52
00:04:31,640 --> 00:04:32,400
Shuyi,

53
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:34,680
marriage is not a game.

54
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:36,560
How can I just agree to this?

55
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:39,880
I don't care who you really like.

56
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:42,240
We'll just put on an act,

57
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,900
husband and wife in name only.

58
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:45,080
If you have someone you like,

59
00:04:45,080 --> 00:04:46,320
you can be with her.

60
00:04:46,520 --> 00:04:48,360
I won't interfere at all. Is that okay?

61
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:49,960
But that would be unfair to her,

62
00:04:49,960 --> 00:04:51,480
and unfair to both of us.

63
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:55,120
But I can't care about that right now.

64
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:58,380
My dad is forcing me to marry someone abroad,

65
00:04:58,560 --> 00:05:00,920
but I don't want to marry a stranger.

66
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:02,400
Jingheng,

67
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:04,520
we grew up together.

68
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:06,120
I know what kind of person you are.

69
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,840
We'll just be a married couple in name only.

70
00:05:07,840 --> 00:05:10,170
Everything else will stay the same, okay?

71
00:05:10,960 --> 00:05:12,640
Shuyi, calm down.

72
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:15,000
I can talk to your father for you.

73
00:05:15,840 --> 00:05:18,120
But asking me to propose to you,

74
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:20,040
I can't do that.

75
00:05:24,840 --> 00:05:26,240
I only see her as a friend,

76
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:29,160
and I definitely wouldn't use marriage as a bargaining chip.

77
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:30,640
So I cruelly rejected her.

78
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:32,680
Later, I found out

79
00:05:33,159 --> 00:05:34,560
that when she was abroad,

80
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:37,360
her relationship with her husband wasn't good.

81
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:39,720
If I had thought of another way back then,

82
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:42,680
she probably wouldn't have suffered so much.

83
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:44,760
Wen Shuyi's dad is really cruel.

84
00:05:44,840 --> 00:05:46,480
She is his biological daughter.

85
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:49,610
Why would he force her to marry someone she doesn't love?

86
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:54,640
Weren't you just saying you were worried?

87
00:05:55,159 --> 00:05:56,760
And now you feel sorry for her?

88
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:58,120
Who's worried?

89
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,800
I'm just purely curious.

90
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:07,800
Curious?

91
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:10,400
Knowing your personality,

92
00:06:10,400 --> 00:06:11,680
if you were curious,

93
00:06:12,280 --> 00:06:13,940
you would have asked long ago.

94
00:06:14,760 --> 00:06:16,560
Holding back until now to ask,

95
00:06:17,440 --> 00:06:19,240
is it because you're jealous,

96
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:20,760
and embarrassed?

97
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:22,040
I'm hungry.

98
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:23,970
I'm going to find something to eat.

99
00:06:32,159 --> 00:06:33,080
I'm hungry too.

100
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:24,400
We found the child you were looking for.

101
00:07:24,400 --> 00:07:26,320
He's been in the orphanage in the suburbs all these years.

102
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:27,120
I got it.

103
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:31,960
Don't be afraid, child.

104
00:07:31,960 --> 00:07:33,120
I mean no harm.

105
00:07:34,960 --> 00:07:36,420
Let me show you something.

106
00:07:41,400 --> 00:07:42,760
The woman in this photo

107
00:07:42,880 --> 00:07:43,760
is your mother.

108
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:46,680
Do you remember what she looks like?

109
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:50,120
Good boy.

110
00:07:59,640 --> 00:08:00,440
Jingheng,

111
00:08:02,440 --> 00:08:05,240
since you insist on staying with Zhixia.

112
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:08,120
Then give me a grandson soon.

113
00:08:08,960 --> 00:08:10,120
So I can rest easy.

114
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:11,560
A grandson.

115
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:12,840
Dad,

116
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:16,340
you'd better take a look at this big grandson first.

117
00:08:16,440 --> 00:08:17,240
Brother,

118
00:08:17,960 --> 00:08:19,960
sister-in-law is not as innocent as you think.

119
00:08:19,960 --> 00:08:21,280
Her illegitimate child with someone else

120
00:08:21,280 --> 00:08:22,400
has grown so big.

121
00:08:22,840 --> 00:08:24,000
This was before she married into our family,

122
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:25,530
who knows who the father is.

123
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:27,360
I was thinking of you.

124
00:08:27,520 --> 00:08:29,580
It took me a long time to find this out.

125
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:31,000
Look at his features.

126
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,480
He looks so much like her.

127
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:34,880
The original host has a child.

128
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:41,480
Shen Zhixia.

129
00:08:42,799 --> 00:08:44,680
Is what Jingxi said true?

130
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:48,280
Then what is going on with this child?

131
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,320
I don't know.

132
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:50,180
You don't know?

133
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:51,640
Shen Zhixia.

134
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:53,800
Right in front of your biological son,

135
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:55,400
you can pretend not to know him.

136
00:08:55,400 --> 00:08:56,520
You are so cruel.

137
00:08:58,160 --> 00:08:58,960
Lu Jingxi,

138
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:00,920
stop talking nonsense here.

139
00:09:00,920 --> 00:09:02,360
I know what kind of person Shen Zhixia is

140
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:03,320
better than you do.

141
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,240
You do?

142
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:06,280
Come on, nephew.

143
00:09:07,160 --> 00:09:07,960
Say Mom.

144
00:09:08,760 --> 00:09:09,280
Say

145
00:09:09,800 --> 00:09:10,640
it.

146
00:09:11,400 --> 00:09:12,240
Say it.

147
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:13,850
What's the argument about?

148
00:09:13,920 --> 00:09:15,520
We'll know once we check.

149
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:17,080
Take the child to the hospital

150
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:18,360
for a paternity test.

151
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:27,960
Press for five minutes.

152
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:29,560
Don't rub to avoid bruising.

153
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:40,020
I'm sorry you have to go through this.

154
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:41,300
Where's the child?

155
00:09:41,640 --> 00:09:42,520
After Dad had his blood drawn,

156
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:44,380
he put him in the car immediately.

157
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:46,080
Leave things here to me.

158
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:47,540
You go back and rest first.

159
00:09:49,880 --> 00:09:50,840
When the results come out,

160
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:52,240
I'll tell you right away.

161
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:53,360
I will definitely prove your innocence.

162
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,040
Okay.

163
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:58,040
Be careful on the way.

164
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:03,900
Leaving in such a hurry, Sister-in-law?

165
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:06,160
Are you afraid that when the results come out,

166
00:10:06,160 --> 00:10:08,560
you won't be able to return to the Lu family?

167
00:10:09,160 --> 00:10:09,960
True.

168
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:12,080
How could the Lu family tolerate

169
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:13,160
such a bastard?

170
00:10:13,520 --> 00:10:14,360
Lu Jingxi.

171
00:10:14,920 --> 00:10:16,480
I used to think you were boring.

172
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:18,040
Now I think you're shameless.

173
00:10:18,040 --> 00:10:20,200
Making a fuss about an irrelevant child,

174
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:21,660
what kind of skill is that?

175
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:26,400
An irrelevant child?

176
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:31,120
I used to think that my brother was ruthless.

177
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:33,840
I didn't expect that in terms of disowning one's relatives,

178
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:35,840
you're even worse, Sister-in-law.

179
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:36,960
When you and that bastard

180
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:38,200
have nowhere to go,

181
00:10:39,040 --> 00:10:41,840
as long as you are willing to lower your head and beg me,

182
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:42,840
I will definitely

183
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:43,760
save a place for you in the Lu family.

184
00:10:43,760 --> 00:10:45,360
Save a place in the Lu family?

185
00:10:45,680 --> 00:10:46,480
Lu Jingxi.

186
00:10:46,920 --> 00:10:47,680
You should figure out

187
00:10:47,680 --> 00:10:49,520
if you have a place in the Lu family yourself.

188
00:10:49,520 --> 00:10:50,400
Leave me alone.

189
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:52,160
Shen Zhixia.

190
00:10:54,920 --> 00:10:56,720
I hope you can still be so tough

191
00:10:57,800 --> 00:10:59,730
after the report results come out.

192
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:14,680
Kid, what's your name?

193
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:16,080
Little Star.

194
00:11:19,680 --> 00:11:21,940
Were you scared at the hospital just now?

195
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:25,100
Why are you burning up?

196
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:27,000
Why didn't you tell us at the hospital?

197
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:28,330
Let's go. I'll take you.

198
00:11:29,880 --> 00:11:30,720
I'm not going.

199
00:11:31,120 --> 00:11:32,600
That grandpa at home

200
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:34,520
was so mean to me at the hospital.

201
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:35,680
I'm not going.

202
00:11:36,680 --> 00:11:37,800
Don't be scared.

203
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:39,320
I'll be here for you from now on.

204
00:11:39,320 --> 00:11:40,720
No one will be mean to you.

205
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:44,240
Mom.

206
00:11:45,360 --> 00:11:46,760
What did you just call me?

207
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:49,080
Now that they're not here,

208
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:51,040
can I call you Mom?

209
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:53,120
I know you're my mom.

210
00:11:53,320 --> 00:11:55,040
I won't admit it.

211
00:11:55,040 --> 00:11:56,720
I won't cause you any trouble.

212
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:57,650
Sister-in-law,

213
00:11:58,760 --> 00:12:00,440
you haven't even read the test results yet,

214
00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:02,160
and you're already acting so affectionate.

215
00:12:02,160 --> 00:12:03,040
Shen Zhixia,

216
00:12:03,760 --> 00:12:05,240
this test result,

217
00:12:05,480 --> 00:12:07,600
you better read it very carefully.

218
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:11,040
This child is yours.

219
00:12:11,120 --> 00:12:14,180
How many more times are you going to lie to the Lu family?

220
00:12:14,720 --> 00:12:16,160
Take this child right now

221
00:12:16,480 --> 00:12:18,010
and get out of the Lu family.

222
00:12:19,160 --> 00:12:20,760
She is not my mom.

223
00:12:20,760 --> 00:12:22,440
Don't kick her out.

224
00:12:22,640 --> 00:12:25,570
Send me back to the orphanage, but don't kick her out.

225
00:12:30,040 --> 00:12:30,800
Dad,

226
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:33,320
this child is indeed pitiful.

227
00:12:33,800 --> 00:12:34,480
But if he stays,

228
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:36,810
who knows how much trouble he'll bring us.

229
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:40,080
Get out.

230
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:44,120
You stay right by my side.

231
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:46,050
You're not allowed to go anywhere.

232
00:12:53,760 --> 00:12:55,920
I can't rewrite the original owner's past,

233
00:12:55,920 --> 00:12:57,680
but Little Star is her child,

234
00:12:58,160 --> 00:12:59,480
a living human being.

235
00:12:59,760 --> 00:13:01,560
I can't throw him back to the orphanage,

236
00:13:01,560 --> 00:13:04,020
nor can I let him suffer any more grievances.

